import React from 'react'
import { Video } from 'grommet'

export const Vid = () => {
    return (
        <Video {...props} key="video" controls="over" fit="cover">
            <source src="./kaaris.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
            <track
    key="cc"
    label="English"
    kind="subtitles"
    srcLang="en"
    src="/assets/small-en.vtt"
    default
  />
        </Video>
    )
}



export default Vid
